data.description:
Welcome Home! This 1960's home has all the charm and modern comforts you are looking for! Enjoy the wood burning fireplace nestled between the living and dining rooms. Interior wood shutters adorn every window. The large Arizona room provides an additional space for relaxation or entertaining guests; the exposed beams add a touch of rustic elegance. Step outside and enjoy the views of the majestic Catalina Mountains or take a swim in the inviting pool. The low care natural desert landscaping ensures easy maintenance. Situated in the central part of town, this home is conveniently located to shopping, dining or enjoying all that Tucson has to offer! Schedule a showing today! Interested in an investment or income opportunity? Read More to find out! Looking for an exceptional investment opportunity in central Tucson, Arizona? Look no further! This fully furnished and stocked property is a TURNKEY gem, ready to start generating income TODAY as a short-term or long-term rental.  
 
Fully Furnished: No need to worry about furnishing the property - it is move-in ready for guests. 
Well-Stocked: The property comes with all the essentials, ensuring a seamless transition to renting. 
Income Potential: With its prime location, this property is in high demand for both short-term and long-term rentals. 
Proven Track Record: This property has been home to guests via VRBO as short-term rentals for those looking to visit Tucson as well as long term rentals to those working in Tucson or transitioning into the area. 
 
Don't Miss Out! Opportunities like this don't come around often. Whether you're an experienced investor or looking to start your real estate journey, this property is your gateway to financial success. 
 
Seize the opportunity to own a fully equipped income-generating property in central Tucson. Your investment future starts here!  
 
*Please Note: All contents, furniture and décor available for purchase on a separate bill of sale.
